{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7caa5334c1","title":"给艾思奋的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6072bd5543","index":0,"year":1938,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"7caa5334c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji11","name":"毛泽东全集第11卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji11.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji11":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3e5cc2df8c","type":"paragraph","text":"给艾思奋的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"7caa5334c1"},{"id":"8f0794be0d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年1月12日）思奇同志：我没有《鲁迅全集》有几本零的，《朝华夕拾》也在内，遍导都不见了军事问题我在开始研究，但写文章暂时还不可能哲学书多研究一会再写还更好些，似不急在眼前几天梁激澳到此，他的《乡村运动理论》有许多怪议论，可去找他谈谈。有空可来谈，但请在显一星五两天以外之晚上敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"7caa5334c1"},{"id":"0b830f4cf4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"7caa5334c1"},{"id":"a593b0b319","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十二日夜[1]梁激溪，1893年生，广西桂林人。20世纪30年代在山东进行过有利于地主阶级的“乡村建设”实验。建国后任政协全国委员会委员、常务委员。[2]这里的《乡村运动理论》，应是《乡村建设理论》。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"7caa5334c1"}],"page":{"id":"4df15fd6b9","publicationId":"maoquanji11","articleId":"7caa5334c1","start":479,"end":479}}}},"__N_SSG":true}